\r\n    支付命令及確定證明書聲請強制執行。\r\n\r\n中    華    民    國    111   年    6     月    10    日\r\n                    民事第九庭司法事務官","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDV/111%2c%e5%8f%b8%e4%bf%83%2c16683%2c20220610%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDV,111,司促,16683,20220610,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"司促","JNO":"16683","JDATE":"20220610","JTITLE":"支付命令"}